text: WayOutWest Records is an independent record label from London. They have made singles and EPs by the following artists: *Cajun Dance Partyhttp://www.xl- recordings.com/news/~cajun-dance-part/?first=1 *Late of the Pier *Video Nasties *Laura Marling WayOutWest also manage a number of bands and solo artists, such as the Cascade Mountain Boys. ==References== Category:Independent record labels Category:British record labels
